caption.body: Today is National Coming Out Day! We honor and celebrate everyone with the courage to speak their truth! The LGBTQI community has come a long way since the days of Harvey Milk, and we cheer you on for working tirelessly to promote and protect human rights. Cohen took this snapshot while staying with Smith and Milk in their apartment above Castro Camera during a visit to San Francisco and fondly remembers it as ‚Äúsimply a lovely moment of time between two lovers, who happened to be my dear friends.‚Äù
